## override_app Actions Reference

| Action | Required Args | What It Does |
|--------|--------------|--------------|
| `set` | `appName`, `url` | Add or update an import-map override (sets localStorage, syncs to panel) |
| `remove` | `appName` | Remove the override from localStorage (panel keeps URL for re-enable) |
| `enable` | `appName` | Re-enable a previously disabled override |
| `disable` | `appName` | Disable an override without removing its URL |
| `reset_all` | — | Clear ALL overrides at once |

After any override change, the extension DevTools panel auto-detects and syncs within ~3 seconds.

## app_action Lifecycle Reference

| Action | What It Does |
|--------|--------------|
| `mount` | Force-mount an app (calls `activeWhenForced(true)` + `reroute()`) |
| `unmount` | Force-unmount an app (calls `activeWhenForced(false)` + `reroute()`) |
| `unload` | Unregister and unload an app completely |

